    "reviews": {
      "1": {
        "name": "Nguyen Thu Ha",
        "desc": "I really love this pants-and-top set! The fabric is soft and breathable, and the fit is very flattering. It works great for both office days and casual outings."
      },
      "2": {
        "name": "Tran Minh Anh",
        "desc": "The dress looks beautiful in person, with neat stitching and true-to-photo color. The silhouette is feminine and comfortable enough to wear all day."
      },
      "3": {
        "name": "Le Phuong Thao",
        "desc": "The wide-leg pants and blouse pair perfectly. The design is modern, easy to style, and suits many body types. I got so many compliments the first time I wore it."
      }
